'adl' is not recognized as an internal or external command- Click start >  right-click Computer > Properties > Advanced system settings  - In Enviroment Variables, scroll down to the one named "Path" and click "edit"   - bring your cursor to the end of the variable value (it should end with a ; )   - Add the path to the bin folder of the Air SDK. ( in your case C:\Program Files (x86)\Adobe\Adobe Flash CS6\AIRSDK\23.0.0.257\bin)  - click ok, ok, then voila!  no need to even restart.  